 - Ô Y hạng - 金陵五題－烏衣巷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-V%C5%A9-T%C3%ADch/author-EjtGFCLaQR-cL2GZdcpbaQ">Lưu Vũ Tích</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nh%E1%BB%AF-D%E1%BB%B1c/K%C3%BD-Tuy%C3%AAn-Ho%C3%A1-%C4%90%C3%A0o-tri-ph%E1%BB%A7-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem--cWnDldvV5CZmMGRCfHtbg">Ký Tuyên Hoá Đào tri phủ kỳ 1 - 寄宣化陶知府其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nh%E1%BB%AF-D%E1%BB%B1c/author-Gb-Ht5DceR7EDVtjdSr3Zw">Phạm Nhữ Dực</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/T%E1%BA%B7ng-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-b%C3%AD-th%C6%B0-C%E1%BB%B1-Nguy%C3%AAn/poem-VMYJn53VQAqdnjD26WFD3g">Tặng Dương bí thư Cự Nguyên - 贈楊秘書巨源</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-C%E1%BB%B1-Nguy%C3%AAn/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-quy-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-%C4%90%C3%B4-k%C3%BD-L%E1%BB%87nh-H%E1%BB%93-x%C3%A1-nh%C3%A2n/poem-eB4b0KvUIIWPAYk_VWfrUg">Tương quy Đông Đô ký Lệnh Hồ xá nhân - 將歸東都寄令狐舍人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-C%E1%BB%B1-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-ujv3_N4k0KkIvWqK4PUlgw">Dương Cự Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-Trung-Dung/U-vi%E1%BB%87n-t%E1%BA%A3o-xu%C3%A2n/poem-H5l6Ko5a_N36MXogpCD7Sw">U viện tảo xuân - 幽院早春</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-Trung-Dung/author-MT45jiON3tr0HzFzTrrtDA">Liễu Trung Dung</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
